# SQL migration files are hashed byte-for-byte by packages/shared-db/src/migrate.ts
# to detect hand-edits. They MUST have stable LF line endings across platforms,
# otherwise Windows checkouts (core.autocrlf=true) rewrite them to CRLF and the
# checksum diverges from the LF hash recorded in core.__platform_migrations,
# crashing server/worker boot with MigrationChecksumMismatch.
*.sql text eol=lf
